com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest.filesystem

Class ErrorReason

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.bindings.ApiEnumeration<ErrorReason>
      • com.vmware.vcenter.vm.guest.filesystem.ErrorReason
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class ErrorReason
extends com.vmware.vapi.bindings.ApiEnumeration<ErrorReason>
    The ErrorReason enumeration class defines the reasons a file or directory operation failed. This enumeration was added in vSphere API 7.0.2.0.

    See enumerated types description.

    See Also:
